name: Eventide
description:
Gloaming within the lattice.

Process: A Sony KV-13FM12, Sony HVC-2400, Sony XV-5000 and Panasonic WJ-MX50A dreaming of each other, through each other. Direct capture reprocessed via Panasonic WJ-MX50A and played back through a Durabrand DCC0903D, rescanned via Nikon D7100 donning a Carl Zeiss Jena Biometar 2.8/80.
